import { AppBar, Container, Typography } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'

const Header = () => {
  return (
    <AppBar color="transparent" position="static">
      <Container>
        <Toolbar>
          <Typography>
            
          </Typography>
        </Toolbar>
      </Container>

    </AppBar>
  )
}

export default Header
